[
  {
    "startTime": 1.0,
    "endTime": 2.3,
    "text": "Coming right up, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.4,
    "endTime": 12.8,
    "text": "Delicious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.7,
    "endTime": 17.2,
    "text": "Wow, that looks like fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.3,
    "endTime": 19.8,
    "text": "I'll have two Krabby Patties, but don't cook them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.9,
    "endTime": 22.099999999999998,
    "text": "I'll have two frozen Krabby Patties, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.2,
    "endTime": 23.099999999999998,
    "text": "Yes, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.2,
    "endTime": 25.099999999999998,
    "text": "I want patty skates."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.2,
    "endTime": 26.8,
    "text": "I need two patties now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.9,
    "endTime": 28.299999999999997,
    "text": "It's beautiful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.4,
    "endTime": 31.799999999999997,
    "text": "I'm selling twice as many patties and I don't even have to cook 'em."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.9,
    "endTime": 36.5,
    "text": "This is the happiest and most cost-effective day of me whole life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.6,
    "endTime": 40.2,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.8,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "How is this possible?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.1,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "I freeze his place solid and he turns it into an ice rink."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.6,
    "endTime": 49.9,
    "text": "He's making more money than ever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 53.8,
    "text": "That's because, unlike you, he's a good businessman."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.9,
    "endTime": 56.9,
    "text": "Well, if it isn't the wind beneath my wings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.0,
    "endTime": 61.8,
    "text": "I don't understand why you don't just steal a Krabby Patty in all that confusion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.0,
    "endTime": 64.9,
    "text": "I'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.3,
    "endTime": 69.7,
    "text": "I don't know why I encourage him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.7,
    "endTime": 74.3,
    "text": "This is fantastic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.4,
    "endTime": 77.4,
    "text": "The local hockey team is payin' me to practice here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.5,
    "endTime": 78.7,
    "text": "Coming through."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.8,
    "endTime": 80.89999999999999,
    "text": "Hi, Patrick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 82.2,
    "text": "Hi, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.1,
    "endTime": 89.5,
    "text": "Where'd the puck go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.1,
    "endTime": 96.19999999999999,
    "text": "Holy shrimp; Plankton!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.7,
    "endTime": 102.7,
    "text": "I did it; I've finally got a Krabby Patty!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.2,
    "endTime": 106.8,
    "text": "Not quite, Plankton, you'll have to get past me first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.9,
    "endTime": 110.60000000000001,
    "text": "There's the puck; that little square guy has it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.7,
    "endTime": 111.4,
    "text": "Get him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.0,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "Yikes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.2,
    "endTime": 116.2,
    "text": "Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 123.9,
    "text": "You're mine now, Plankton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.9,
    "endTime": 128.70000000000002,
    "text": "You won't get away with this, Plankton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.8,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "Hey, SpongeBob, long time no see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.1,
    "endTime": 133.1,
    "text": "What you been up to? How was your weekend?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.2,
    "endTime": 136.2,
    "text": "Oh, my weekend was fabulous, thank you for asking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.3,
    "endTime": 138.5,
    "text": "Patrick and I went jellyfishing, but I lost my net."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.2,
    "endTime": 142.6,
    "text": "So, I tried to borrow one from Squidward, but he didn't have one, and then when he yelled at me, he swallowed a bug."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.2,
    "endTime": 145.6,
    "text": "- Swallowed a bug.  - Fascinating."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.1,
    "endTime": 148.4,
    "text": "- Well, gotta go.  - Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.5,
    "endTime": 151.1,
    "text": "Better luck next time, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.5,
    "endTime": 153.1,
    "text": "There's the puck, E, get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.6,
    "endTime": 168.79999999999998,
    "text": "Hold it right there, mister."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.7,
    "endTime": 193.39999999999998,
    "text": "Yes, I'm gonna make it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.4,
    "endTime": 205.70000000000002,
    "text": "Gotcha, Plankton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.8,
    "endTime": 207.3,
    "text": "On the contrary..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.4,
    "endTime": 209.70000000000002,
    "text": "It is I who has you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.3,
    "endTime": 213.8,
    "text": "The clamboni."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.9,
    "endTime": 215.20000000000002,
    "text": "Run for it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.5,
    "endTime": 222.5,
    "text": "Run, you fools, run!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.0,
    "endTime": 234.0,
    "text": "It's working."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.1,
    "endTime": 237.7,
    "text": "I'm actually going to get a Krabby patty!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.1,
    "endTime": 244.29999999999998,
    "text": "Come on, get out of the way!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.4,
    "endTime": 246.3,
    "text": "You're blocking the exit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.7,
    "endTime": 254.2,
    "text": "No, no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.1,
    "endTime": 257.1,
    "text": "I'll take that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.7,
    "endTime": 261.3,
    "text": "Brilliant idea to block the exit with your body, SpongeBob."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.4,
    "endTime": 262.7,
    "text": "Um, thank you, Mr. Krabs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.4,
    "endTime": 266.5,
    "text": "You lose again, Plankton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.9,
    "endTime": 269.09999999999997,
    "text": "I'm not giving up yet, Krabs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.2,
    "endTime": 271.7,
    "text": "I've still got my secret weapon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.6,
    "endTime": 274.20000000000005,
    "text": "The thermostat!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.1,
    "endTime": 277.3,
    "text": "Thermostat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.4,
    "endTime": 282.29999999999995,
    "text": "That's right, Krabs, it was I who froze the Krusty Krab."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.4,
    "endTime": 283.2,
    "text": "You see?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.4,
    "endTime": 287.29999999999995,
    "text": "You gone too far this time, Plankton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.4,
    "endTime": 295.09999999999997,
    "text": "You can pummel me employees, try to destroy me restaurant, but nobody messes with me thermostat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.0,
    "endTime": 305.0,
    "text": "See, Krabs? You can't defeat me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.4,
    "endTime": 334.5,
    "text": "Here's your Krabby Patty and lemonade, Mr. Krabs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.6,
    "endTime": 335.6,
    "text": "Thank you, lad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.1,
    "endTime": 339.20000000000005,
    "text": "Well, well, if it isn't Plankton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.6,
    "endTime": 340.70000000000005,
    "text": "You know, I should thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.8,
    "endTime": 346.7,
    "text": "What, with the ice rink and now the swimming pool gimmick, I'm making more money than I ever did with the old Krusty Krab."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.8,
    "endTime": 349.2,
    "text": "Hey, you got any more good ideas?"
  }
]